short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Proxy helper for remotely accessing you Taisun Gateway from the Chrome Browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension can be used with the Taisun.io gateway container located here: 
https://hub.docker.com/r/taisun/gateway/
It allows you to define the Https Proxy endpoint using the URL generated here: 
https://api.taisun.io/prod/genurl

If you are an experienced user you can manually modify your own proxy settings, this only exists as a helper to provide a single click to hop into your servers local network and access your Docker containers from a remote location.
